name: Purple Valley Maze
description:

Started as an AR experience, you can dive into this magical world where all green items are turned into purple ones in real time
 
People from all over the globe choose to use the ‘Purple Valley’ effect on a daily basis, with more than 150 million photos being taken since the filter’s release on over 60 countries
 
Now, with so much energy gathered around Earth, we can open the portal to Purple World
